+ *
+ * Implements comprehensive security headers using Helmet.js:
+ * - Content Security Policy (CSP)
+ * - HTTP Strict Transport Security (HSTS)
+ * - X-Frame-Options
+ * - X-Content-Type-Options
+ * - X-XSS-Protection
+ * - Referrer-Policy
